# Connecteurs

## Didacticiel

### Implication

A, B, C |- A -> B -> A
A, B, C |- A -> (A -> B) -> B
A, B, C |- (B -> C) -> (A -> B) -> (A -> C)

### Conjonction

A, B, C |- A -> B -> A && B
A, B, C |- A -> B -> C -> A && (B && C)
A, B, C |- (A && B) -> (C -> A)
A, B, C |- (A && B) -> (C -> B)
A, B, C |- (A && B) -> (B && A)

### Disjonction

A, B |- A -> A || B
A, B |- B -> A || B
A, B, C |- B -> A || (B || C)
A, B |- A || B -> (A -> B) -> B
A, B |- A || B -> (B || A)

### Négation

A |- false -> ~A
A |- ~A -> A -> false
A |- A -> ~~A
A |- false -> A
A, B |- ~A -> A -> B

## Exercices

### Basiques

A, B, C |- A && B -> C -> A
P, Q, R |- P && Q -> R -> Q && R

### Logique constructiviste

A, B |- A -> A && (A || B)
P, Q, R |- P || (Q && R) -> P || Q
A, B |- A || B -> (A -> B) -> B
A, B, C |- (A -> B -> C) -> ((A -> B) -> A -> C)
P, Q, R |- (P -> Q -> R) -> P && Q -> R
A, B, C |- (A -> B) -> (A -> C) -> A -> B && C
A, B, C |- (A -> B) -> A || C -> B || C
A, B |- (A && B) || (A || B) -> A || B
A, B, C |- (A -> C) && (B -> C) -> A || B -> C
A, B |- ~A || B -> A -> B
A, B, C |- (A -> B -> C) -> A && B -> C
P, Q, R |- P -> (P -> Q) -> ((P -> Q) -> (Q -> R)) -> R
A, B, C |- (A && B -> C) <-> A -> B -> C
A, B, C |- (A || B -> C) <-> (A -> C) && (B -> C)

### Associativités

A, B, C |- A && (B && C) <-> (A && B) && C
A, B, C |- A || (B || C) <-> (A || B) || C

### Raisonnements

A, B |- (A -> B) -> (~B -> ~A)

### Négations

P, Q, R |- P -> (R -> ~Q) -> (P -> Q) -> ~R
P, Q |- (P -> Q) && (P -> ~Q) -> ~P
A, B |- (A || ~B) && B -> A
P, Q |- ~P || Q -> P -> Q

### Distributivités

P, Q, R |- P && (Q -> R) <-> P && Q -> P && R
P, Q, R |- P && (Q || R) <-> (P && Q) || (P && R)
P, Q, R |- P || (Q && R) <-> (P || Q) && (P || R)
P, Q, R |- P -> (Q && R) <-> (P -> Q) && (P -> R)
P, Q, R |- P -> (Q || R) <-> (P -> Q) || (P -> R)
P, Q, R |- (P -> (Q -> R)) <-> ((P -> Q) -> (P -> R))

### Relations

A, B, C |- (A || B -> C) <-> (A -> C) && (B -> C)

# Infinite loop

P, Q, R |- P || (Q -> R) -> (P || Q) -> (P || R)
A, B, C |- (A -> C) || (B -> C) -> (A && B -> C)